# Weather App

A simple weather application that displays current weather conditions for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API.

## Features

- Fetches and displays current weather data for a searched city.
- Displays city name, temperature, weather icon, description, humidity, and wind speed.
- Dynamically updates the background image based on the searched city's name.
- Simple and intuitive user interface.

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- [OpenWeatherMap API](https://openweathermap.org/api)


## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Before you begin, ensure you have met the following requirements:

- You have a web browser installed.
- You have an internet connection.

### Installation

1. Clone the repository to your local machine:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/weather-app.git
